title: Apple’s earnings next week may set a Nasdaq record
text: (By Rodrigo Campos, Reuters) – The Nasdaq 100 index, dominated by U.S. technology stocks, may set a record high next week, helped by good earnings from Apple Inc expected on Tuesday.
